href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-judas-priest-kick-off-north-american-tour-leg-in-montreal-3793828">混合表演了《无敌之盾》和九张经典专辑中深受粉丝喜爱的曲目</a>。</p><p>最近，乐队贝斯手 Ian Hill 表示 Judas Priest <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priest-are-re-mixing-and-re-releasing-their-debut-album-rocka-rolla-3789975">正在重新混音他们的首张专辑《Rocka Rolla》，该专辑刚刚成立 50 周年</a>：“我相信它很快就会发行。距离发布只有几周了，我确定……它将被重新发布，这是个好消息。它终于得到了一直需要的产品。”</p><p>在其他地方，哈尔福德最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priests-rob-halford-on-coming-out-its-never-too-late-to-set-yourself-free-im-fucking-here-im-queer-get-fucking-used-to-it-3788982">回顾了 1998 年他在 MTV 现场表演时如何出柜</a>，他说：“释放自己永远不会太晚，因为我们知道，一旦你出柜，攻击就会消失。我他妈的就在这里，我很奇怪，他妈的习惯吧！”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judas-priest-announce-europe-2025-tour-dates-3809505">Judas Priest 宣布 2025 年欧洲巡演日期的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
保罗·麦卡特尼回忆起“才华横溢”的昆西·琼斯：“认识他我感到很荣幸” https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-remembers-supremely-talented-quincy-jones-i-felt-privileged-to-have-known-him-3809499?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=保罗-麦卡特尼-记得才华横溢的昆西-琼斯，我觉得有特权认识他Surej SinghTue, 05 Nov 2024 01:50:54 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3809499 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他在场时我们总是很开心，他的传奇将持续多年”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-remembers-supremely-talented-quincy-jones-i-felt-privileged-to-have-known-him-3809499">保罗·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 回忆起“才华横溢”的昆西·琼斯 (Quincy Jones)：“我很荣幸认识他”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/paul-mccartney-quincy-jones@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>向他已故的朋友、传奇制片人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quincy-jones">昆西·琼斯</a>致敬——看看麦卡特尼下面是怎么说的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/quincy-jones-obituary-3809386">昆西·琼斯，1933-2024：眼中闪烁着光芒打破界限的超级制片人</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（11月4日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/legendary-producer-and-songwriter-quincy-jones-has-died-aged-91-3809203">昆西·琼斯去世的消息</a>震动了乐坛。他的公关人员证实，这位传奇制片人已于 11 月 3 日星期日在家人陪伴下去世。</p><p>现在，麦卡特尼在 20 世纪 60 年代初第一次见到琼斯，在社交媒体上发表了一篇长文向这位已故制片人致敬。在帖子中，马卡回忆起通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>制作人乔治·马丁介绍给琼斯的经历，以及他“非常积极、充满爱心的精神”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3809312" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809312" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809312" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Paul-McCartney-and-Quincy-Jones.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_WireImage.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Paul-McCartney-and-Quincy-Jones.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Paul-McCartney-and-Quincy-Jones.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Paul-McCartney-and-Quincy-Jones.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Paul-McCartney-and-Quincy-Jones.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Paul-McCartney-and-Quincy-Jones.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Paul-McCartney-and-Quincy-Jones.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809312" class="wp-caption-text">保罗·麦卡特尼和昆西·琼斯。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>麦卡特尼写道：“亲爱的昆西·琼斯去世了，让我们这些认识他的人感到悲伤。他非常有才华，我很荣幸能认识他很多年。他是披头士乐队制作人乔治·马丁的朋友，两人共同创作了一些非常优秀的音乐。</p><p> “昆西（Quincy）或‘昆斯’或‘Q’，正如他所知道的那样，他的眼睛里总是闪烁着光芒，并且有一种非常积极、充满爱心的精神，感染了每个认识他的人。当然，他与迈克尔·杰克逊的合作是传奇，他的音乐弓还有很多其他的弦乐。”</p><p> “我对他的主要回忆总是我们分享的私人时刻，我永远不会停止感谢南希总是安排我们在洛杉矶时拜访他。这些访问既有趣又鼓舞人心，”麦卡特尼继续说道。 “但作为一个朋友，我想记住他。我们总是在他面前玩得很开心，他的传奇将持续多年，但我将永远怀念那些我们有幸与这位伟人共度的私人时刻。”</p><p>请参阅下面麦卡特尼的完整帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DB9d894MT1T/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><